OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, then drier and brighter
OL,7,Fconditions spread east before a narrow
OL,8,Fband of rain follows. Late afternoon
OL,9,Fmost western places become dry with
OL,10,Flate sunshine. Strong winds likely
OL,11,Falong the coast this morning, then
OL,12,Feasing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClear spells for a time this
OL,15,Fevening, with temperatures quickly
OL,16,Ffalling and perhaps some patchy mist.
OL,17,FThen cloud increases with showers or
OL,18,Flonger spells of rain arriving. Also
OL,19,Fbecoming breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
